* smartphones
  * don't load your gpg key on your smart phone!

* browser plugins?
 * adblock
 * umatrix
 * https everywhere
 
 * start page instead of google

* on a public machine:
    * use privacy mode
    * always log out from services
    

* on a windows machine:
    * antivirus software: keep up to date, run regularly
    * firewall


